# Environment & commands
- Always use the interpreter at `./.venv/bin/python`.
- Prefer `micromamba` with `-p ./.venv -c conda-forge`.
- Use `pytest -q` for tests; `ruff check` for lint; `black .` for formatting.

# Layout
- Code in `src/yourpkg` (rename via scripts/init.sh), tests in `tests`, config in `.vscode/`.
